lead_paragraph: Lewis Hamilton cruised to an unchallenged victory in Sunday’s German Formula One Grand Prix to extend his lead over Mercedes team mate Nico Rosberg at the top of the world championship standings.

headline.print_headline: Hamilton Wins in Germany to Extend Championship Lead
